edu.stanford.services.explorecourses

Class Section

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.services.explorecourses.Section

  • public class Section
extends java.lang.Object
    Sections represent offerings of a course (or lab/discussions associated with the course). A section will have a particular instructor and meeting schedule. Students enroll in sections.
